document_data.History:
Born in [[1346 DR]], Princess Alicia was the eldest daughter of High King [[Tristan Kendrick]] and the [[druid]] [[Robyn Kendrick]]. Groomed during her early years by the kingdom's [[archmage]] [[Keane]], Alicia became an adventurer in [[1365 DR]].

During the {{YearlinkName|1365}}, Alicia was briefly granted the powers of an [[avatar]] by the [[Earthmother]], in order to defeat the [[dracolich]] [[Gotha]], a servant of [[Talos]] who attacked the Moonshae Isles.

She died unexpectedly in the {{YearlinkName|1407}}, and was widely believed to have been [[poison]]ed by agents of [[Lionel Carrathal]]. Her death prompted a series of insurgencies in [[Callidyrr]], which were swiftly quelled by the [[Callidyrr dragoon]]s.{{Cite dragon/405/Heroes of the Moonshaes|5}}
